				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "\n\nAutomated testing is a",
					"messageId": "msg_d28653dc8001puBT5H5vp6DoMc"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " cornerstone of software quality because it provides fast, repeatable, and reliable verification that code",
					"messageId": "msg_d28653dc8001puBT5H5vp6DoMc"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " behaves as intended. Unlike manual testing, automated tests can be run on",
					"messageId": "msg_d28653dc8001puBT5H5vp6DoMc"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " every change — catching regressions the moment they're",
					"messageId": "msg_d28653dc8001puBT5H5vp6DoMc"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " introduced rather than days or weeks later. They serve as living documentation of expected behavior, making it safer for",
					"messageId": "msg_d28653dc8001puBT5H5vp6DoMc"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " developers to refactor and evolve a codebase with confidence. A well-maintained test suite reduces",
					"messageId": "msg_d28653dc8001puBT5H5vp6DoMc"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " the feedback loop between writing code and discovering defects, which lowers the cost of fixing bugs and prevents",
					"messageId": "msg_d28653dc8001puBT5H5vp6DoMc"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " them from compounding. Ultimately, automated testing shifts quality assurance from a",
					"messageId": "msg_d28653dc8001puBT5H5vp6DoMc"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " reactive gatekeeping activity into a continuous, integrated part of the development process.",
					"messageId": "msg_d28653dc8001puBT5H5vp6DoMc"
				},
